  "texts": [
    "The manner that news is distributed and consumed has significantly changed with the advent of the digital age.",
    "Images have become a crucial component of this new environment because of their innate capacity to concisely express complex storylines.",
    "They frequently contain important information that supplements textual content and occasionally even replaces it.",
    "However, creating news stories manually from photos is a time-consuming task that requires a lot of labor and knowledge.",
    "Traditional machine learning (ML) algorithms have limitations with the uniform data format, but integrating more than one type of data is the need of the hour."
  ],
